a. Calibration method
In an attempt to overcome this issue, we use the insight from the analytical treatment to correct for this through post-processing.
1. The first step is to take samples from the identity capacitance matrix as a baseline (usually configuration 0 of the capacitor bank in the unit cells, with all couplings turned off).

